{
  "name": "RPlog_A_Leak",
  "title": "A Leak",
  "summary": "In the hangar bays of a frigate, the spy Zeak Oppenhiemer hosts a covert briefing for two New Republic-aligned guests -- the ambassador Ambrosia Delgard and the former StarOps officer Drax Rendolen -- after his thirteen-year-old daughter Ara te Dannaan flies them in aboard a modified Mantaray. Once everyone is settled, Zeak explains that the Imperial Lord Thel approached him to perform a covert service for the Empire, and he has chosen to leak the details to the Republic instead. He hands his guests data cards and shares his impressions of the cruel, inexperienced Imperial contact, along with the operational intelligence that the target ship -- the Pleasure Palace -- is crewed largely by R6 and M-3PO droids. Ambrosia wrestles with the grim logic of the situation while Drax fixes on the droid vulnerability with a devious grin. The ambassador closes by standing, bowing solemnly, and thanking Zeak for the personal risk he has taken in passing the leak along.",
